				<div class="col-lg-6  text-justify">
				<h1 class="shead-style text-center">JHARKHAND</h1>
				<p>For a long time Jharkhand has been there for the recognition from a wider perspective. A state home to one of the highest amount of scheduled tribes is also home to many reserved forests and wildlife sanctuaries. The landscape of Jharkhand is magnificent due to a number of reasons. These reasons include its geographical position, annual rainfall, flora, fauna and the climate it faces throughout the year. </p><p>
        Many of its major tourist locations include waterfalls, caves, hill sides and temples. One of the most important prime locations is the Jain pilgrimage Centre at Parasnath hill. It attracts many local and global visitors due to its location and surrounding. </p><p>
        For travelers Jharkhand is the place where they get see its magnificent national parks and protected natural areas.
        </p>
